Integration with Telecom Applications. The Services may contain features designed to interoperate with
Telecom Applications. To use such features, You may be required to obtain access to such Telecom Applications
from their providers, and may be required to grant Us access to Your account(s) on such Telecom Applications. We
cannot guarantee the continued availability of such Service features, and may cease providing them without entitling
You to any refund, credit, or other compensation, if for example and without limitation, the provider of a Telecom
Application ceases to make the Telecom Application available for interoperation with the corresponding Service
features in a manner acceptable to Us.
Name: Integration with Telecom Applications
